help.data: JSON Dict to respond with. Ex. ?data={"color": "red"}. Data is returned as "data" key.
help.sleep: Changes the time to delay in seconds. Ex. ?sleep=5. Defalut is 0. Sleep can NOT exceed 5 seconds and must be > 0!
help.status: Status code to simulate in response. Ex. ?status=500. Default is 200.
help.basic_auth: Prompt user with Basic Auth challange. Ex. ?auth=username:password.
